OL,6,FActress Amanda Abbington has said she
OL,7,F"would not have been able to live with
OL,8,Fmyself" if she had stayed silent about
OL,9,Fher Strictly Come Dancing experience.
OL,11,FThe 50-year-old, who left the show
OL,12,Fearly in 2023, said she thought "long
OL,13,Fand hard" before making a complaint to
OL,14,Fthe BBC about the behaviour of former
OL,15,Fdance partner Giovanni Pernice due to
OL,16,Fthe "backlash" she would receive.
