OL,6,FPernice, who has rejected "any
OL,7,Fsuggestion of abusive or threatening
OL,8,Fbehaviour", will not return to the
OL,9,Fshow this year, and said in a
OL,10,Fstatement on Instagram in June that he
OL,11,Fis "cooperating fully" with an ongoing
OL,12,F"BBC investigation".
OL,14,FSpeaking to the Sun On Sunday, the
