OL,6,F"I had to think long and hard about
OL,7,Fmaking a complaint because I knew the
OL,8,Fbacklash I would get. But I would not
OL,9,Fhave been able to live with myself for
OL,10,Ffuture people going on that show.
OL,12,F"I know what happened in that room,
OL,13,Fit's on video and I have no problem
OL,14,Fwith anyone seeing that. It's a duty
OL,15,Fof care that is needed."
OL,17,FShe added: "Rehearsal rooms should be
OL,18,Fa safe space, there is a duty of care
OL,19,Fand kindness, and that courtesy wasn't
OL,20,Fextended to me on this job.
