OL,7,Finterview with the Sunday Times that
OL,8,Fthe show was "tough and horrible".
OL,10,FIn a statement posted on his Instagram
OL,11,Fin May, Pernice said he rejected the
OL,12,Faccusations and wanted to clear his
OL,13,Fname.
OL,15,F"Those who have followed my journey on
OL,16,FStrictly Come Dancing over the last
OL,17,Fdecade will know that I am passionate
OL,18,Fand competitive," wrote the 33-year-
OL,19,Fold, who has been a professional on
OL,20,Fthe dancing show since 2015.
