OL,6,FDi Prima said in a statement that he
OL,7,Fdeeply regrets "the events that led to
OL,8,Fmy departure from Strictly".
OL,10,FEarlier in the week his spokesman Mark
OL,11,FBorkowski told the PA news agency that
OL,12,Fhe had been left "in a very vulnerable
OL,13,Fstate" after "the deluge of
OL,14,Fcommentary, too often without context
OL,15,For nuance".
OL,17,FIn a social media post former Love
OL,18,FIsland star McDermott said she had
OL,19,F"wrestled with the fear of opening
OL,20,Fup", fearing "public backlash" and
OL,21,F"victim shaming".
